; 闘技大会開始～祝勝会まで



;■闘技大会

;◇イベント01・闘技大会に出場決定
*tournament_1

; サファイアシティ
@saveon
@w05
@bg f=0019
@mu f=trick
@fg c=ライナス f=05
[texton w=1]
[ライナス f=05]「Hey, [テオ]!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
I was suddenly stopped by Linus.[k]
I hope he don't start picking a fight again...[k]
[テオ f=12]「Hey, what do you want?」[k]
@fg c=ライナス f=01
[ライナス f=01]「You guys, enter the next tournament.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Huh...?」[k]
Linus suddenly ordered me to participate in a competition.[k]
...Even if you say that, we have our own plans. We're not going to follow your instructions out of the blue.[k]
[テオ f=10]「Sorry, but we...」[k]
[ライナス f=01]「You have no right to refuse. Because your participation has already been accepted.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What?!」[k]
[ライナス f=02]「I decided to let you guys participate. I have connections with the tournament organizers...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh, no...」[k]
How selfish... How can such high-handedness be allowed?[k]
[ライナス f=02]「If you withdraw from the competition, your reputation will plummet, as a party that ran away from the challenge.」[k]
[ライナス f=03]「Well, even if you do participate, we in Hawk Wing will beat you guys to a pulp, so your reputation will go down anyway! Hahahaha!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
What a nuisance... Is there no way to avoid this?[k]
@st

[   if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh019 f=07]「Let's do it, Captain!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd019 f=07]「Let's do it, Captain!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve020 f=07]「Let's fight! Captain!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs021 f=07]「Let's fight! Captain!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg012 f=08]「Captain... Let's fight...!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]

@mu f=tower
[   if exp='ELF2'][クレア２ v=ve021 f=15]「That's right! With our current abilities, we can definitely win!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL2'][マルエット２ v=vs022 f=15]「That's right! With our current abilities, we can definitely win!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM2'][リム２ v=vh020 f=07]「Yeah! We can definitely win!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA2'][フレデリカ２ v=vd020 f=07]「Yeah! We can definitely win!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO2'][ミューズ２ v=vg013 f=08]「That's right... We can win now...!」[k]
[endif]

Surprisingly, our members were eager to accept the challenge.[k]
[if exp='game.party.members.count > 4']
	[テオ f=05]「Does everyone else feel the same way?」[k]
	When I asked that question, the other members nodded in unison.[k]
[endif]
[リーゼル v=vl122 f=08]「I also want to test our current abilities...! I believe that we can definitely put up a good fight against Linus and his team...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I never thought I would hear such powerful words from Riselle...[k]
Everyone else is also very motivated. Before I knew it, everyone seemed to have become very energetic.[k]
There's no doubt that we've grown considerably compared to before. We won the battle at the kobold fort, and it's clear that we're more than a match for them.[k]
Actually, I was thinking that it was about time I tested my strength. This offer might not be so bad.[k]
[ライナス f=01]「...It seems like you're motivated now.」[k]
[ライナス f=03]「But you guys are no match for us! We'll show you your place in front of a large audience! Hahahaha!」[k]
@cl
With those parting words, Linus left.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
To be honest, I'm still not sure how far I can go with my current abilities, so if anything, I feel more like this is a problem.[k]
But...[k]

[   if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs023 f=15]「It's okay! I won't lose to people like that!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve022 f=15]「It's okay! I won't lose to people like that!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd021 f=07]「It's okay! We definitely won't lose to them!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh021 f=07]「It's okay! We definitely won't lose to them!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg014 f=08]「It's okay...! I won't lose to people like that...!」[k]
[endif]

[   if exp='DWA2'][フレデリカ２ v=vd022 f=07]「Let's show them how strong we are!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM2'][リム２ v=vh022 f=07]「Let's show them how strong we are!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL2'][マルエット２ v=vs024 f=08]「I'll get them back for that! I'll make them regret making fun of us!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF2'][クレア２ v=ve023 f=08]「I'll get them back for that! They will regret mocking us!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO2'][ミューズ２ v=vg015 f=08]「We'll show you our power...!」[k]
[endif]

The party is motivated, so let's take a chance and give it a try.[k]
It's not that I don't have any reservations, but sometimes we need to take on ambitious challenges. We can't grow unless we take on tasks that are a little challenging.[k]
Furthermore, even if we lose, we won't have our property confiscated or members taken away, unlike in a duel. The only price would be a small participation fee.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
The date is [b]next Sunday[/b]. I need to make sure I'm fully prepared by then.[k]
We should finish off anything we planned to do. I want to get a good night's sleep the day before, so I'll return to Sapphire City by [b]Saturday[/b] and prepare for the tournament.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
[townoff]


;◇イベント02・大会前日・リーゼルを探しに行く
*tournament_2

; サファイアシティ・大会前日
@eval exp='game.party.removeMember(o.リーゼル)'
@w05
[texton w=0]
[テオ f=06]「Tomorrow is finally the day. I need to make sure I'm fully prepared for the tournament.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Wait, where is Riselle?」[k]
I noticed that Riselle was missing. Maybe she went off somewhere?[k]
[テオ f=05]「Let's see if I can find Riselle.」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント03・公園でリーゼルと会話
*tournament_3

; 公園
@saveon
@bg f=0018
[texton w=1]
[リーゼル v=vl123 e=ローブ,木の杖 f=15]「Ha!」[k]
[テオ e=通常 f=05]「Riselle?」[k]
I found Riselle at the back of the park.[k]
Riselle, what are you doing there all alone...? I approach her.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl124 f=15]「Ahhh!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Riselle!」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル e=ローブ,木の杖 f=06
[リーゼル v=vl125 f=05]「Oh, Captain...」[k]
When I called out to her, Riselle noticed me.[k]
[テオ f=02]「Riselle, what are you doing here?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl126 f=13]「Um... Well... Practicing snowstorm magic...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Snowstorm magic? Does that mean you've mastered [emb exp='o.ブリザード.displayName']?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl127 f=14]「Y-yeah...」[k]
Next to her was a [emb exp='o.ブリザード.displayName'] spellbook. On its cover were magical characters indicating that it had been used, and thus learned.[k]
[テオ f=01]「That's amazing! You really can do it if you try. You overcame a real challenge!」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=09
[リーゼル v=vl128 f=09]「Well... Actually, about that...」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
@bg f=0018 b
@fg c=リーゼル e=ローブ・大 f=10
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=05]「You've learned it, but you can't cast it?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl129 f=10]「Yeah... No matter how many times I try, it doesn't work... I just can't get the blizzard to appear...」[k]
It seems that Riselle kept on trying to learn [emb exp='o.ブリザード.displayName'], and she finally managed.[k]
But even after doing so, she still can't cast it. Imagining the blizzard makes her panic and her mind goes blank.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl130 f=10]「I'm sorry, but in the end, I couldn't do it at all...」[k]
[テオ f=01]「That's not true! Just learning it is a big step forward! It was pretty tough, wasn't it?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl131 f=06]「Y-yeah...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「You did a great job. Well done.」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=25
[リーゼル f=25]「...」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=22
[リーゼル v=vl132 f=22]「Yeah... Thanks, Captain.」[k]
She muttered, with a slightly shy smile.[k]
[テオ f=01]「But you don't have to go through so much pain to master [emb exp='o.ブリザード.displayName']... There are other spells, and I and everyone in the party will support you.」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=02
[リーゼル v=vl133 f=01]「I know, and that makes me happy... But...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl134 f=02]「I wanted to be useful to everyone in the party. I didn't want to just be helped by everyone, I wanted to help everyone. And...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「And?」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=24
[リーゼル v=vl135 f=24]「I didn't want to waste this magic book... Because it was the first gift I ever received from you.」[k]
Saying that, Riselle lovingly hugged the used [emb exp='o.ブリザード.displayName'] spellbook.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle...!」[k]
I was touched that she thought so highly of my gift...! I was so moved that I was at a loss for words.[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=01
[リーゼル v=vl136 f=01]「That's why I want to be able to use this magic someday... I don't know when that will be, though.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「A-ah, you can definitely do it.」[k]
There is still a long way to go, but we have definitely taken a step forward. There is hope on the horizon![k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

@gameon
@eval exp='game.party.entry(o.リーゼル)'
[texton w=0]
[テオ f=02]「Well, it's about time to go back to the inn.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl137 e=ローブ f=02]「Yeah.」[k]
I took Riselle back to the inn.[k]
Tomorrow is finally the first day of the tournament. I need to get back to the inn early and get some rest.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=マックス e=通常 f=06
[texton w=1]
[マックス f=06]「Hey, [テオ]...」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Hey, it's Max. Long time no see.」[k]
Max was waiting in front of the inn. [k]
[テオ f=01]「How's it going at Hawk Wing? Are you going to compete in the tournament? We might end up facing each other.」[k]
[マックス f=06]「...I'm not participating in the tournament.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「What? Why? I heard Hawk Wing was going to compete.」[k]
[マックス f=06]「...」[k]
[マックス f=06]「...Actually, I got fired from Hawk Wing.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What?!」[k]
[リーゼル f=12]「...!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「R-really?」[k]
[マックス f=06]「Yeah. I was suddenly fired yesterday. They said I didn't have to go with them from today.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh no...」[k]
[マックス f=09]「...I guess Linus wanted to radically reshuffle the members to strengthen the team. In order to win this weekend's tournament.」[k]
[マックス f=09]「...I think it was around the middle of last week. Suddenly, new adventurers started joining Hawk Wing's party one after another. And they were all high-level, skilled adventurers.」[k]
[マックス f=09]「I had a feeling something was up, then yesterday, they fired five members at once, including me.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Oh, no...」[k]
[マックス f=09]「We're no longer needed. That bastard Linus... He's been exploiting us...」[k]
[テオ f=10]「That's awful...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl138 f=12]「So, what happened to Maria?」[k]
[マックス f=05]「Maria is going to keep working for them. Linus seems to really like her, and she wanted to stay too. Linus is a good payer, after all.」[k]
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
[マックス f=19]「Well, I was employed as a temporary party member, and I figured my contract would end eventually, so it's fine.」[k]
[マックス f=09]「But I feel sorry for the other girls who were dismissed. They'd worked so hard for Linus all this time...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
@fgf c=マックス f=01
[マックス f=03]「Well, that's why I'm returning to [emb exp='game.party.displayName']! I'll be counting on you again!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...About that, Max, I can't let you rejoin us right now.」[k]
@fgf c=マックス f=11
[マックス f=11]「Whaaaat?! Why?!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「It's stipulated in the guild rules. Parties participating in the tournament aren't allowed to accept new members from one week before the tournament.」[k]
[マックス f=10]「S-seriously...?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Unless there are some restrictions on member transfers, fairness in the tournament cannot be maintained.」[k]
Linus probably recruited new adventurers last week in order to avoid violating those rules.[k]
[テオ f=02]「So please wait until after the tournament is over to join.」[k]
@fgf c=マックス f=01
[マックス f=01]「So I can join after the tournament ends? Then there's no problem!」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Good luck in the tournament! I'll be cheering you on from the stands!」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@eval exp='o.リーゼル.moveHeart(o.テオ, 5)'
[eventoff]


;◇イベント04・大会当日
*tournament_4

; 宿泊後・当日
[texton]
Today is finally the day of the tournament.[k]
Our party members have been working hard. The time has come to show the results of their efforts.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Everyone! Are you ready? Then let's head to the arena!」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


*match_start
; トーナメント戦闘開始処理
@eval exp='game.inDuelBattle = true'
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false gameover=true stopbgm=true
@anime_duel_sign visible=false
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery()'

@return

;◇イベント05・闘技場に入る～１回戦
*tournament_5

; 闘技場の前
@saveon
@mu f=tower
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I stand in front of the arena. The battle to determine the strongest party is about to begin.[k]
[テオ f=05]「All right! Let's do our best!」[k]
I said those words, which were out of character for me, to encourage myself.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl139 f=01]「Hehe... Captain, you seem really motivated.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah. I'm pretty serious about winning this tournament.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl140 f=06]「Weren't you troubled at first when Linus decided to enter us in the competition without asking you?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yes, I was. But things are different now.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Although we ended up participating in an unexpected way, I'm now glad that I am able to participate in this competition.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl141 f=05]「Eh... Why is that?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Earlier, I told you about how I used to be dominated by a man named Blue and was constantly abused.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「When I started my adventure full of dreams, what awaited me was a reality dominated by the strong, one that I could not resist. At that time, I was made painfully aware of how weak and powerless I was.」[k]
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I was driven by the thought that, being weak, I would never be able to do anything in my life... I even thought that maybe I should just quit being an adventurer.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「But I still want to be a strong adventurer... I want to become strong and leave my mark on the world... Yes, that's what I strongly believe now.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl142 f=05]「Captain...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I am not a powerless person. I want to prove that. That's why I think this tournament is a great opportunity to overcome my past self.」[k]
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I want to win this tournament. Then I can be confident as an adventurer... I won't have to be afraid of Blue's shadow anymore...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...But to do that, I need everyone in the party to cooperate. I can't win on my own. Except for Max, the current party members are the first people I've ever truly trusted.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「When we were in Bravetown, Max and I were isolated and helpless, but now we have reliable friends... Including you.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl143 f=05]「Captain...!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Riselle, let's win together! And let's prove that we are not weaklings!」[k]
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl144 f=03]「...Yeah, I understand. Let's work hard together, Captain!」[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w05

; 闘技場・控え室
@saveon
@bg f=0023
@mu f=guild
[texton w=1]
[name n=Attendant]「It's [emb exp='game.party.displayName'], isn't it? You are already registered, so please come in.」[k]
We were led to the waiting room of the arena. Here we would wait for our turn.[k]
In the waiting room, the parties that have already arrived are doing warm-up exercises and holding strategy meetings.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Are these people our rivals...?」[k]
Sixteen teams are participating in this tournament. It seems that there are significantly fewer participating parties than usual.[k]
Apparently, rumors that Linus' Hawk Wing would be entering put many parties off signing up.[k]
Hawk Wing is, regardless of its true nature, considered to be a powerful party. So they must have thought winning was impossible.[k]
Due to these numbers, there are only four matches in all; the first round, second round, semifinals, and final. Winning all four will win the championship.[k]
According to the tournament bracket, we are in a different block from Hawk Wing, so we won't face each other until the final. Of course, that assumes that neither of us is eliminated first.[k]
Although there are few matches, they feature some fairly well-known parties other than Hawk Wing. Every match is intense, so we can't let our guard down. We have to stay focused.[k]
@fg c=ライナス f=01
[ライナス f=01]「Hey, looks like you didn't run away after all.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Linus appeared at the venue. As usual, he looked down on us with contempt.[k]
[ライナス f=01]「I'll give you credit for not running away. But either way, you guys are destined to crawl before me.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...You'd better make sure not to lose before you even fight us.」[k]
[ライナス f=02]「Heh, there's no need to worry. Things have changed now.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?」[k]
[ライナス f=01]「I'm looking forward to fighting you guys.」[k]
@cl
Linus left with some cryptic words.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Things have changed...?[k]
Is there something going on? Or is it just a bluff? It might be better to be cautious just in case.[k]
@se f=door1
[name n=Attendant]「[emb exp='game.party.displayName'] party, we're about to start the first round, so please come to the arena!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Ah, yes, we're on our way.」[k]
It's finally here. We'll do whatever it takes to win and advance to the finals![k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w1

; 闘技場・１回戦
@eval exp='game.backScreen.loadImages(%[storage: "other_arena", visible: true])'
@mu f=brave
@gameon fade
@saveoff
[texton]
[name n=Commentator]「Let's begin the first round! The first match is [emb exp='game.party.displayName'] vs. the Slime Squad! Both sides, step forward!」[k]
[name n="Enemy Leader" f=slime_green]「...! (←Uncharacteristically filled with murderous intent)」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What a murderous aura...! But I can't lose. I'll definitely win!」[k]
[textoff]
@w05
@anime_duel_net visible=true storage=other_arena_net
@w05
[texton]
[name n=Commentator]「In the name of the Duel God, let us start the first match of the first round! Begin!」[k]
[textoff]

