;◇イベント06・２回戦
*tournament_6

; 闘技場・２回戦
[texton]
[name n=Attendant]「Ah, it's the [emb exp='game.party.displayName'] party. Please come in.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000
@eval exp='game.backScreen.loadImages(%[storage: "other_arena", visible: true])'
@mu f=brave
@gameon fade
@saveoff
[texton]
[name n=Commentator]「Now, let's begin the first match of the second round![r][emb exp='game.party.displayName'] vs. Team Amazoness!」[k]
[name n=Amazoness f=valkyrie_yellow_04]「Don't underestimate us just because we're all women, or you'll regret it!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Of course not. We're mostly women too, after all. I'll give it my all!」[k]
[textoff]
@w05
@anime_duel_net visible=true storage=other_arena_net
@w05

; 戦闘・２回戦
@eval exp='game.curTeam = o.チーム・アマゾネス'
@monster pos=1 name=シューター
@monster pos=3 name=チャンピオン
@monster pos=5 name=グラディエイター
@monster pos=9 name=ハイプリースト
@monster pos=11 name=アークメイジ
@call target=*match_start

; 勝利
[texton]
[name n=Commentator]「Congratulations on winning the second round! Please wait until the semifinals begin.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1
@bg f=0023
@mu f=city
@saveon
[texton]
[リーゼル v=vl145 f=05]「We won again...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「That's how strong we've become. It's the result of everyone's hard work up until today.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「But I'm not satisfied with just this much. Our goal is to win the championship. Let's keep winning!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl146 f=01]「Yeah, let's do our best next time too, Captain!」[k]
Riselle's voice was cheerful. She no longer sounds like the the timid girl from when we first met.[k]
Suddenly, I realized that Riselle was encouraging me. She was no longer just someone I needed to protect, but also a reliable friend.[k]
With her by my side, I was sure we could win. For some reason, that's how I felt.[k]
[textoff]
