Suddenly, I felt a sharp tingling sensation throughout my entire body![k]
[テオ f=10]「Guh!」[k]
@se f=dosa
@quake time=500 hmax=10 vmax=5
Unable to move, I collapsed on the ground in front of my enemy![k]
[テオ f=09]「What... is this...?!」[k]

[   if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs029 f=18]「Eek...!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve028 f=18]「Eek...!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh027 f=18]「Eek...!」[k]
