[elsif exp='SYL2'][マルエット２ v=vs030 f=12]「I can't move my body...!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA2'][フレデリカ２ v=vd028 f=12]「I can't move my body...?!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM2'][リム２ v=vh028 f=12]「I can't move...!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO2'][ミューズ２ v=vg020 f=12]「I can't move...!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=09]「Everyone...!」[k]
Everyone fell, one after another.[k]
[テオ f=09]「This symptom is... paralysis?」[k]
It seems that our party members have been paralyzed all at once.[k]
...Paralysis has no natural recovery time, so it's extremely dangerous if it happens to multiple members at the same time. If it happened in a dungeon, it could lead to total annihilation.[k]
[name n="Enemy Mage" f=summon_01]「It seems to have worked out well. As expected of my basilisks.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Basilisks...?!」[k]
@fg a=lizard_yellow left=150 top=360 b
@fg l=lizard_yellow left=350 top=360 b
@fg c=lizard_yellow left=550 top=360 b
@fg r=lizard_yellow left=750 top=360
[name n=Basilisk f=lizard_yellow]「∗growl∗」[k]
When I looked behind me, I saw several lizard-like monsters licking their lips as they watched us, unable to move.[k]
...They're the ones who paralyzed us...![k]
@cl b
@fg c=rich_green left=450 top=40
[name n="Enemy Mage" f=summon_01]「I am a summoner. I summoned monsters behind you, without you noticing.」[k]
[name n="Enemy Mage" f=summon_01]「I am particularly fond of basilisks and salamanders. I trained these creatures well...」[k]
[name n="Enemy Mage" f=summon_01]「While I distract the enemy, they quickly paralyze them.」[k]
[name n="Enemy Mage" f=summon_01]「You guys were so angry at being made fun of that you didn't pay any attention to what was going on behind you. Thanks to that, the plan worked out so well it was laughable.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Damn...!」[k]
So we fell right into the enemy's trap...! What a disaster...![k]
If things continue like this, defeat is certain. I don't want to lose here. What should I do...?![k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=08
[リーゼル f=08]「...」[k]
[name n="Enemy Mage" f=summon_01]「Huh? One of them can move... Why? I'm sure the basilisks bit all of them...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Riselle...!」[k]
I could see Riselle standing alone to the rear.[k]
Riselle was safe...! She was the only one who didn't charge at the enemy. Her cautious nature had unexpectedly paid off.[k]
However, it's unlikely that Riselle alone can take on the summoner and his beasts. The situation remains critical.[k]
[name n="Enemy Mage" f=summon_01]「Well, that's fine. She's only a weak-looking female mage. Come, salamanders, burn them all with your flames!」[k]
@fg a=lizard_red left=150 top=360 b
