The enemy salamanders slowly crawl towards us, targeting us where we lie.[k]
[テオ f=10]「Ugh...!」[k]
Oh no...! Salamanders have a special fiery breath attack. If we get hit by that, we're done for.[k]
Damn... Isn't there any way to turn this around...?![k]
[name n=Salamander f=lizard_red]「Kwaaah!」[k]
[name n=All]「...!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Damn...!」[k]
The salamanders all opened their mouths wide, preparing to breathe fire![k]
Is it over...?![k]
[リーゼル v=vl148 f=07]「Ahhhhh!」[k]
