; 戦闘に勝利
@mu f=happy
[texton]
Amazing! It was a tough opponent, but we managed to win! All thanks to Riselle![k]

[if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh029 f=03]「Riselle, that was amazing!」[k][endif]
[if exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd029 f=03]「Riselle, you're amazing～!」[k][endif]
[if exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve030 f=15]「You did it! We won today thanks to you!」[k][endif]
[if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs031 f=15]「You're quite something. To be honest, I've changed my opinion of you.」[k][endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg021 f=02]「This victory was only thanks to Riselle...」[k][endif]

@fg c=リーゼル f=29
[リーゼル v=vl151 f=29]「Well... I didn't do anything special...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「There's no need to be modest. There's no doubt that you saved everyone this time.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl152 f=33]「Um, well... Thank you, everyone...」[k]
Riselle is very shy when everyone praises her. Her entire face is red, and she looks very cute.[k]
[テオ f=02]「It's amazing that you were able to cast [emb exp='o.ブリザード.displayName'] at such a critical moment. You couldn't do it before, no matter how hard you tried.」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=06
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl153 f=06]「...Captain, you said you definitely wanted to win this tournament, right? You said you wanted to get stronger and gain confidence. You said you wanted to overcome your oppressed past.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Y-yeah...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl154 f=08]「When I heard that, I wanted to win for your sake... I wanted to win and give you confidence.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle...!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl155 f=06]「I wanted to be useful to you... You've always helped me... You've always been kind to me...」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=01
[リーゼル v=vl156 f=01]「You know... I feel like I finally found my place in this party...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl157 f=01]「Here, I feel like I can be useful and overcome my weaknesses...! That's how I started to feel. And it's all thanks to you always supporting me...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Well... I don't know...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl158 f=01]「I wanted to make you happy by helping our team win...! With that thought in mind, I was able to overcome the terror of a blizzard. Even a coward like me was able to do my best.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl159 f=04]「And once I had... I could cast it a second time as well. I'm glad I mustered up the courage...!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Riselle...」[k]
Is that so? For my sake, Riselle overcame her fear of blizzards...![k]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you, Riselle. I'm so happy to hear that, I don't know what to say...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl160 f=01]「Captain, let's definitely win. I'll do my best next time too. I'll be useful to you.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes! Let's all win together! We can do it!」[k]
[name n=Commentator]「Congratulations on winning the semifinals!」[k]
[name n=Commentator]「Next up is the final match! Please wait until the match begins.」[k]
