; 闘技場・控え室
@bg f=0023
@mu f=guild
@saveon
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=01]「All right! It's finally the final round!」[k]
We made it through to the semi-finals and finally made it to the finals. One more win and we'll be the champions of the tournament.[k]
Until recently, becoming champions would have seemed like something from a different world. It is the result of each member of the team working hard and improving their skills. As captain, I am truly proud of them.[k]
@fg c=ライナス e=通常 f=01
[ライナス f=01]「...I'm impressed you made it. I thought you'd crash out quickly.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Our opponents in the final are Linus and Hawk Wing. They advanced smoothly through the tournament.[k]
To be honest, given what happened at Kobold Fortress, I thought it would be difficult for them to reach the final in their current weakened state. Contrary to my expectations, they ended up being our opponents in the final.[k]
[ライナス f=01]「I'll make you eat your words in the final. Look forward to it.」[k]
@cl
Leaving behind that parting remark, Linus left.[k]
@fg c=マリア e=通常 f=02
[マリア v=va111 f=02]「It's been a while, guys.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Maria...!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl161 f=05]「Maria...!」[k]
Maria spoke to me. She remains a member of Hawk Wing, so is one of my opponents in the final match.[k]
[マリア v=va112 f=02]「I never thought I'd end up fighting you guys.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Maria, I'm sorry, but we're not going to go easy on you.」[k]
[マリア v=va113 f=02]「I understand. I won't slack off either. I'm a member of Hawk Wing now, after all. I'll fulfill my responsibilities.」[k]
[リーゼル f=05]「...」[k]
[マリア v=va114 f=10]「I'm sorry, Riselle. I really don't want to fight you, but...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl162 f=08]「I understand. I don't really want to, but I'll fight with all my might. So Maria, give it your all too.」[k]
[マリア v=va115 f=03]「I see! ...Hehe, you've become quite strong since I last saw you, Riselle.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl163 f=05]「I wonder if that's true...」[k]
[マリア v=va116 f=01]「Well, I'm going to go now. Let's do our best, Riselle, Captain ♪」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yes, I'm looking forward to the match.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「Well, the match is about to start...」[k]
There is little time left. We must prepare thoroughly for battle while we still can.[k]
@se f=door1
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「Hello...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「...」[k]
Suddenly, two adventurer women entered our waiting room.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Ah... you guys are...」[k]
They're the female adventurers from Hawk Wing who tried to steal our glory at Kobold Fortress before. Why are they here...?[k]
[テオ f=05]「Ah, your dressing room is over there. Go back to the stairs and take the passageway on the opposite side...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「No... We're not participating in the battle...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What? Is that so?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「We... left Hawk Wing.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What?!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「We were kicked out of the party right before the tournament started. Linus announced that he would be making major changes to the party in order to strengthen it.」[k]
Come to think of it, Max mentioned something like that...[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「After we lost to you guys... Linus said we were useless...」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Oh no...」[k]
That's so cruel. They've been devoted to Linus all this time...[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_06]「But now I feel refreshed. I was tired of being Linus's nighttime companion. With a fresh start, I want to find a new job.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I see... That's good to hear.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「Anyway, we came here today to tell you guys in [emb exp='game.party.displayName'] something important.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Something important...?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「Hawk Wing has changed from the party we described the other day. With a major change in members, it's become a completely different team.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「A different team...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「Before firing us, Linus invested all of his remaining funds in hiring a whole bunch of skilled adventurers.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「It's now much stronger than before. Don't underestimate them.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「Be especially wary of the red-haired male warrior. He can kill with a single blow, as well as counterattack. He should be your priority target to defeat with magic or other means. Please be very careful.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I understand. I'll keep that in mind. Thank you for coming to give us your advice.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「We tried to attack you before... We wanted to make up for it.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「From now on, I want to be an adventurer who everyone can rely on, without resorting to underhanded tactics... Like you guys.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Good luck to both of you!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_01]「Yes!」[k]
[name n=Attendant]「The match starts in 10 minutes. Please get ready soon.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「It's finally here...!」[k]
If I win this battle, I will confess my feelings to Riselle.[k]
I had been thinking about it for a long time. Once I became a full-fledged adventurer, I would confess my feelings to her.[k]
This tournament is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity. I will prove my strength in this battle and become a man worthy of Riselle![k]
[テオ f=06]「Let's go...!」[k]
I clenched my fists tightly and headed toward the arena with a secret determination.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w1

