Cheers and praise for us echo from all around.[k]
Since forming a few months ago, we have worked hard together every day. And now, we have finally achieved this wonderful honor.[k]
This will instantly raise our popularity and reputation. We are now closer than ever to becoming an ideal party of adventurers.[k]
And I'm not the same person I used to be. I overcame my weaknesses and became a strong adventurer.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl165 f=02]「You've worked hard, Captain.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah, I guess so.」[k]
Riselle looked happier than ever before.[k]
She also went through a series of misfortunes as an adventurer, but now that she's here, has she finally been rewarded?[k]
