[texton w=1]
[マックス f=03]「Let's toast our victory in the fighting tournament!」[k]
[name n=All]「Cheers!」[k]
[マリア v=va117 f=03]「Congratulations, everyone!」[k]
On the night of the final match, we in [emb exp='game.party.displayName'] decided to rent out a restaurant in town and hold a victory party to celebrate winning the tournament.[k]
Incidentally, Max and Maria aren't party members, but they are participating as well.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Yay! Let's drink tonight!」[k]
[マリア v=va118 f=07]「Max! Why are you the most excited one here?! You didn't do anything at all today!」[k]
[テオ e=通常 f=01]「Ahaha...」[k]
They're outsiders, and Maria is even a member of the enemy team, but if they can liven up the party, that's fine. They both have cheerful personalities.[k]
[リーゼル e=通常 f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Huh? Riselle, are you a little nervous?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl167 f=09]「I... I'm not good at drinking parties...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「In that case, it's best to eat slowly at your own pace. The most important thing is to enjoy yourself.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl168 f=01]「Yeah... That's right. You're right.」[k]
