[リーゼル v=vl169 f=01]「Yeah... Thank you.」[k]
[マリア v=va119 f=08]「Hmm? Aren't you two getting a little cozy?!」[k]
; ↑ 文句つける雰囲気で絡んでくる（ちゃかす感じではない）
Maria, who was already feeling a little tipsy and in a good mood, started chatting with Riselle and me.[k]
[テオ f=12]「W-what is it, Maria...?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl170 f=13]「No, that's not true... It's just your imagination...」[k]
[マリア v=va120 f=07]「Don't lie! You guys weren't that close before!」[k]
