If Maria says so, it means that we seem closer. Maybe Riselle feels closer to me than I thought. If that's the case, I'm happy.[k]
However, just becoming close friends is meaningless. I want to date Riselle as a woman.[k]
That's why tonight, I have to do what I have to do...[k]
