[texton]
When the victory party was in full swing and things had calmed down a bit, I took Riselle outside.[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=05
[リーゼル v=vl172 f=05]「What's wrong, Captain? Why are you suddenly taking me away?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Well, I have something I want to talk about... Let's take a walk.」[k]
With a pleasant evening breeze blowing, Riselle and I walk alone together.[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=02
[リーゼル v=vl173 f=01]「We... really won the tournament... It still feels like a dream.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「It's not a dream. We really did win. It's the result of your and everyone else's hard work.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl174 f=05]「Captain...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Everyone has become stronger. Riselle, everyone else, and me too... I feel like I can overcome my past now. It's all thanks to everyone.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl175 f=02]「Me too... I may not be able to become like Grandma, but right now I think I can become a full-fledged mage. Thank you, Captain.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Well... I haven't really done anything...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl176 f=04]「Everyone in the party said they were glad they followed the captain. And so am I...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl177 f=01]「Let's keep working hard together, Captain.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「...Ah!」[k]
At first, she ended up accompanying me by chance, but now I am really happy that we can fight together.[k]
Now... she has become the woman I love.[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=05
[リーゼル v=vl178 f=05]「By the way, what did you want to talk about...?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Ah, um... Well...」[k]
Come on, be brave. You have to convey your feelings.[k]
[テオ f=10]「...!」[k]
I made sure no one was around, took a deep breath, and turned to face her.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle. I have something to give you.」[k]
[name f=other_01]I took Riselle's hair ornament out of my pocket and showed it to her.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl179 f=12]「...! This is...!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I'll return it to you, Riselle.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl180 f=05]「Why do you have it? I'm sure it was being sold in the store...」[k]
[テオ f=01]「I bought it. It's your important hair ornament, isn't it?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl181 f=09]「But the price was so high...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Don't worry about it.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl182 f=09]「But...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「You know... When your hair ornament was taken, you looked really sad...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I... didn't want to see you sad...」[k]
[リーゼル f=25]「...」[k]
Riselle gazes at me and the hair ornament with moist eyes.[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=23
[リーゼル v=vl183 f=23]「Thank you, Captain... I'm so glad I got to be with you...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I'm glad, too.」[k]
I put the hair ornament back in Riselle's hair.[k]
