; 翌日・街角でリーゼルと待ち合わせ
@bg f=0019
@mu f=city
[texton]
Today, I decided to give everyone in the party a day off and take a break from adventuring work.[k]
Of course, I wanted everyone to get some rest, but it's also for my own convenience.[k]
[テオ e=通常 f=05]「Riselle, are you here yet?」[k]
Yes, I decided to go on a date with Riselle today.[k]
I'm currently waiting for her at a corner of the town street. Standing alone at the edge of the street, I wait for Riselle to arrive.[k]
[テオ f=10]「She isn't here...」[k]
Just then, I began to worry whether she would really come.[k]
@fgf c=マックス e=通常 f=03
[マックス f=03]「Hey, [テオ]!」[k]
[テオ f=11]「Ahh!」[k]
Suddenly, Max called out from behind me.[k]
[テオ f=10]「What's up, Max? Don't scare me like that...」[k]
@fg c=マックス f=01
[マックス f=01]「What are you doing here?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「N-Nothing much...」[k]
I have an important first date with Riselle coming up. Don't bother me.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Hey, [テオ], I heard.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「What are you talking about?」[k]
[マックス f=03]「You started dating Riselle, right?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Gah!」[k]
How does Max already know?![k]
[マックス f=01]「What's going on? Are you dating? Well?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Well, that's...」[k]
[マックス f=03]「It's true! I see, I see! You finally have a girlfriend...」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
Well, Max can know... It'll come out eventually anyway.[k]
[マックス f=04]「So, how far did you go with her?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「How far? With what?」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Don't play dumb! I'm talking about how far your relationship with Riselle has progressed!」[k]
@fg c=マックス f=22
[マックス f=22]「...Did you already do something naughty?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「No, I wouldn't do that!」[k]
[マックス f=03]「What, not yet? But you've kissed her, right?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
@fg c=マックス f=05
[マックス f=05]「...Hey, you guys haven't even kissed yet? What's up with that? You guys are so shy!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「There's no way I can do all that all of a sudden... I have to think about her feelings...」[k]
[マックス f=05]「If you keep saying things like that, she'll never let you do anything! It's better to be a little pushy! Women actually want that too!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「That's just your opinion.」[k]
[マックス f=06]「Now, it's just my hunch, but Riselle seems like the type who would easily agree to have sex if you asked her nicely.」[k]
Max... Don't say things that send a chill down my spine...[k]
@fg c=マックス f=03
[マックス f=03]「Just go for it! I'm rooting for you, okay? As your best friend!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I appreciate the sentiment, but...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl192 e=通常 f=01]「Captain!」[k]
@cl b
@fg l=マックス f=03 b
@fg r=リーゼル f=01
Suddenly, Riselle came running over to me.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Oh, look who it is. I'll get out of the way! Good luck! Let me know how it goes!」[k]
@cl l
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
Really, that Max...[k]
@cl b
@fg c=リーゼル f=05
[リーゼル v=vl193 f=05]「Were you talking to Max?」[k]
[テオ f=13]「N-no, it's nothing!」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=01
[リーゼル v=vl194 f=01]「We're going to the park in Sapphire City today, right?」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Yeah. Well, let's get going then.」[k]
